      "content": "but being alive just feels like a punishment. it's like i'm forced to keep existing in a world that he isn't part of. sometimes i wonder if he's more peaceful now that he's gone, and if there's even a point to me struggling through this alone. it feels like there's no way to actually fix this emptiness, just a way to stop feeling it.",
